     <tr>
          <td>Raw</td><td>The raw DN value. </td>
     </tr>
     <tr>
          <td>RadianceStandard</td><td>The standard conversion factor from DNs to radiance. </td>
     </tr>
     <tr>
          <td>RadianceScaleFactor</td><td>An adjustment factor for each filter.</td>
